{
  "stem": "24195.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's like gates, you know, steel gates.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you-- guards standing around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sending us up to a room where there's an older police officer in, in civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Turns out, when I show him the summons, he's totally speechless.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He doesn't he's-- doesn't know what to-- how to react to it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It turns out that he is not a member of the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He is a regular homicide or police officer, a detective, that they pulled in because all the henchmen are out executing the-- they executed scores of them of all the-- over at the headquarters, army headquarters in Berlin, executing all the ones that they suspected of being part of that assassination plot of Hitler.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was my luck, because if they had been a regular guy, he goes over to some file cabinet, picks my summons, looking for my name.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, that was, like I said, before computers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they never communicated this incident that we didn't show up, the Gestapo in this other-- in Silesia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we did-- he, he can't find anything, so he hands me back the summons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he says, I can't find anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You did the right thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You came back, and you reported.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And if we want you, I'm sure they're going to contact you again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So never anything happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We got out of that building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know how thankful I was going through all those gates and guards, guard checkpoints, and getting out of there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My mother and I looked at us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We couldn't understand why because we hadn't heard about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We hadn't heard that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was in the morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
